{"title":"庐山诗夏（二首）","authors":["张兆华"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"庐山诗夏（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张兆华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花径"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——怀白司马山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走向幽美的花径"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口吟“长恨春归无觅处”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去探寻乐天大师宽广的心境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁盛的花草、错落的石板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有醉人的“景白亭”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远溯悠远的年代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰辛的骚人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里赏花写诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却喊出了那个时代的乐音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含鄱口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——寄友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我疑惑我自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是置身海岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怀疑我视觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五老峰似成了熟悉的村寨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我甚至嫉恨我的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎么在这时向我走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦哦，这儿是海岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在观云海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿正是生我的村子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是奶奶故事里的狼孩么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿还站着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有你和这含鄱口一样的胸怀"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}